      • readWelcomeMessage

        public java.lang.String readWelcomeMessage()
        It is a method which can read Welcome message from WelcomeMessage.txt
        返回:
        WelcomeMessage The random selected welcome message.

      • goWelcome

        public void goWelcome()
        a method to show the first user interface. which contains random selected welcome message and a ordering button for customers to order dish.

      • goMainMenu

        public void goMainMenu()
        a method to generate the main menu user interface which contains six buttons for costumers to order dishes

      • goDishPage

        public void goDishPage(java.io.File myfile)
        a method show the matched sub menu when user select a kind of dishes. it shows more details of the main menu.
        参数:
        myfile - A type of File which the GUI choose to read.

      • writeDishInfro

        public void writeDishInfro(java.io.File myfile)
        a method renew the dish information in the original files.
        参数:
        myfile - A type of File and clarify which file need to be renew.

      • goNextConfirm

        public void goNextConfirm(int total,
                          java.io.File userFile)
        a method which show the confirm information of ordering which contains continue to order and waiting for food buttons
        参数:
        total, - userFile Total: the total price of a user. userFile: show ordering detail on the interface to tell costumer what he/she orders.
        total - Total: the total price of the bill.
        userFile - The dish information of the costumer ordered.

      • tellJoke

        public void tellJoke()
        a method shows telling joke interface after costumer finish order and waiting for serving dishes.

      • leavingPay

        public void leavingPay()
        a method shows the bill details after the costumer choose to leave

      • readFareWellMessage

        public java.lang.String readFareWellMessage()
        a method can read file of farewell message.
        返回:
        fareWellMessage. The random selected farewell message from farewell file.

      • sayByebye

        public void sayByebye()
        a method will show the last user interface. which contains a label shows bye-bye message and a finish button.

      • goSleep

        public void goSleep()
        a method when the robot is inactive for 30 seconds. it will go a sleeping mode. and show a message dialog to warn user. it can be waked up for any time.
